        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/17/2/9/1",
        "text": [
          " حديثه ضعف، وفي مذهبه ارتفاع. ويروي الصحيح والسقيم، وأمره مختلط."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.tashayyu": [
            "9 – Ibrāhīm b. Isḥāq, al-Aḥmarī, known by the kunya Abū Isḥāq.  al-Nahāwandī.  In his ḥadīths there is weakness, and in his madhhab there is irtifāʿ. He narrates both the authentic and the weak, and his matter is mixed."
          ]
        }
      }
